OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774144984
OL,3,CScottish Government appoints group to
OL,4,Ccreate memorial for Queen Elizabeth II
OL,6,FSenior figures from across Scottish
OL,7,Fpublic life have been appointed to a
OL,8,Fgroup set up to propose a permanent
OL,9,Fmemorial in Scotland to honour Queen
OL,10,FElizabeth II, the Scottish Government
OL,11,Fhas announced.
OL,13,FThe Scotland Legacy Group will make
OL,14,Frecommendations to the First Minister,
OL,15,Fwho will take the ideas to the King.
OL,17,FFunding for the memorial in Scotland,
OL,18,Falong with similar projects across
OL,19,FBritain, will be met by the UK
OL,20,FGovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
