CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774144984
OL,3,CScottish Government appoints group to
OL,4,Ccreate memorial for Queen Elizabeth II
OL,6,FDr Joseph Morrow, the Lord Lyon King
OL,7,Fof Arms, will chair the group.
OL,9,FHe will be joined by: Dr Anna Keay,
OL,10,Fmember of the Queen Elizabeth Memorial
OL,11,FCommittee and director of the Landmark
OL,12,FTrust; St Andrews modern history
OL,13,FProfessor Chandrika Kaul; retired
OL,14,FLieutenant Colonel Johnny Stewart;
OL,15,FLeonie Bell, director of V&A Dundee;
OL,16,FAnne Lyden, director general of the
OL,17,FNational Galleries of Scotland; and
OL,18,FHelen Webster, deputy director for
OL,19,Fcabinet, parliament and governance and
OL,20,Fsecretary for commissions at the
OL,21,FScottish Government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774144984
OL,3,CScottish Government appoints group to
OL,4,Ccreate memorial for Queen Elizabeth II
OL,6,FCulture Secretary Angus Robertson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Queen Elizabeth meant so much
OL,8,Fto so many people in Scotland and it
OL,9,Fis right that we pay tribute to her
OL,10,Fremarkable 70-year reign and life of
OL,11,Fpublic service.
OL,13,F"The scenes as Her Majesty's cortege
OL,14,Fmade the journey from Balmoral Castle,
OL,15,Fwhere she died, to the Palace of
OL,16,FHolyroodhouse, demonstrated how much
OL,17,Fshe was loved in the country where she
OL,18,Fspent so much of her private time.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774144984
OL,3,CScottish Government appoints group to
OL,4,Ccreate memorial for Queen Elizabeth II
OL,6,F"I am very grateful to the group for
OL,7,Ftaking this opportunity to deliver a
OL,8,Ffitting tribute from the people of
OL,9,FScotland to Her Majesty The Queen."
OL,11,FDr Morrow said: "I am honoured to have
OL,12,Fthe opportunity to develop and advise
OL,13,Fon a Scottish memorial to Queen
OL,14,FElizabeth to celebrate her
OL,15,Fextraordinary reign and dedicated life
OL,16,Fof public service.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@cO]sD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774144984
OL,3,CScottish Government appoints group to
OL,4,Ccreate memorial for Queen Elizabeth II
OL,6,F"I am determined to create the space
OL,7,Ffor a truly Scottish memorial and
OL,8,Fdelighted to be working alongside such
OL,9,Fa talented group of individuals to do
OL,10,Fso.
OL,12,F"The group will engage with
OL,13,Fcommunities across the country to
OL,14,Fallow us to envisage a Scottish
OL,15,Fmemorial and a lasting symbol of
OL,16,Fremembrance and gratitude for the late
OL,17,FQueen.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
