OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774144984
OL,3,CScottish Government appoints group to
OL,4,Ccreate memorial for Queen Elizabeth II
OL,6,F"Queen Elizabeth had a deep affinity
OL,7,Ffor Scotland, and it is a privilege to
OL,8,Fcreate a legacy that can inspire
OL,9,Fgenerations to come."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@UO]
